Package ca.mcgill.ecse321.gameorganizer.models

Class Game

java.lang.Object
ca.mcgill.ecse321.gameorganizer.models.Game
@Entity public class Game extends Object
Represents a board game in the system. Games can be owned by users and borrowed by others through borrow requests. Each game has information about player counts, an image, and when it was added to the system.
